{"tid":389242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Why Not HK? Apple為風災災民提供免費維修","createTime":"2017-09-06T05:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T10:40:42.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83dce1e33db239244aac27e3fbe56c4b0ddc7447","tid":389242,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:31:24.000Z","msg":"Apple 在風災後不但馬上啟動捐款機制協助救災，同時亦非正式地為受影響的災民免費維修 iPhone。雖然 Apple 沒有官方宣佈，但部份受影響的災民將被浸壞的 iPhone 拿到 Apple Store 維修，店方都為他們提供免費維修。之前流出的內部文件，說明了手機浸濕一般都不在免費維修之列，今次 Apple 算是低調地做了好人好事，為需要擔憂食物、食水和住宿的災民減少一件困擾的事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/09/06/free-iphone-repair-for-hurricane-harvey-victoms/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2Ffree-iphone-repair-for-hurricane-harvey-victoms%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=7hiTfe62AKfRJLUG5Et5Q49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c4ffb046\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/09/06/free-iphone-repair-for-hurricane-harvey-victoms/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"b092cc1acd33b7d5c62ae8fe7bf266b71195514f","tid":389242,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:32:15.000Z","msg":"Apple歧視港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9aa84105e7ba9d56cac7f55125a5de44cb3a10a","tid":389242,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"美國公司緊係要盡本土責任"},{"pid":"a782d7a3d288b2d0ad68c9cdb083993bc1a6eb71","tid":389242,"uid":22054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:49:30.000Z","msg":"香港冇事喎，馬交就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cf82a89bb057ec5be9d0b03a90ed4bb991e54f","tid":389242,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T07:14:58.000Z","msg":"此post作廢，冇星"},{"pid":"7555bcfb67bf47c5eed6149